headline: Home Depot 'Has Upside' As Earnings Outlook Improves, Sales Accelerate
summary: Home Depot narrowed 2024 guidance early Tuesday after beating earnings and sales estimates for the third quarter.  Home Depot stock fell in a buy area.  The home improvement store giant is now guiding a 1% decline in adjusted earnings per share for the full year vs. its prior forecast for a 1%-3% drop.

headline: Lowe's Companies, Inc. to Host Third Quarter 2024 Earnings Conference Call on Nov. 19
summary: Lowe's Companies, Inc. (NYSE: LOW) announced today that it will hold its Third Quarter 2024 Earnings Conference Call at 9 a.m. Eastern time on Tuesday, Nov. 19. A webcast will be available by visiting the Quarterly Earnings section of the Lowe's Investor Relations website, ir.lowes.com. Supplemental materials will be available 15 minutes before the start of the conference call.
